('truck', '180mm Paris V2 50° Matte Black Longboard Skateboard Truck', 22, 'https://www.muirskate.com/photos/products/5499/hd_product_Paris-180mm-V2-Matte-Black-%28Set-HD%29.png', 'Paris redesigned their top selling longboard trucks to bring us the new and improved Paris V2! These trucks feature a beefier hanger that is less prone to bending from all of the abuse you can dish out.The Paris V2s still have a very open, unrestrictive bushing seat that works well for those who enjoy a very carvy, surfy feeling setup. Paris also improved the design by throwing in more durable pivot cups and adding a little extra length to the kingpin.These trucks look as great as they ride! A thick powder coat not only protects the aluminum hangers and baseplates from the elements but also creates a beautiful, glossy finish. No matter what your color preference, Paris has got you covered!'),
