('truck', '166mm Aera K5 Raw Precision Longboard Skateboard Trucks', 216, 'https://www.muirskate.com/photos/products/7855/hd_product_Aera-K5-Raw-176mm_42deg-Downhill-%28SET-HD%29.png', 'The Aera K5 Trucks have landed! Featuring a new sleek design, the same gangster lean, and narrower widths, the Aera K5 is one of the most trusted trucks in the game. With a hanger width of 158mm, and a number of different threaded axle options, you can be sure you''ll get the exact feel your looking for. Trucks assembled with 4140 Steel Axles and grade 8 kingpins.'),
('truck', '187mm Gullwing 10" Sidewinder II Lime Longboard Skateboard Truck', 47, 'https://www.muirskate.com/photos/products/7605/hd_product_Gullwing-Sidewinder-II-Green-%28Pair-HD%29.png', 'If you are looking for exaggerated easy turning and a smooth flow, the Gullwing Sidewinders are definitely the trucks for you. Designed to surf the street, the Gullwing Sidewinders simulate the movements that are common to surfing on an actually wave in the ocean! Surfing the desert is now possible!'),
('truck', '187mm Gullwing 10" Sidewinder II Black Longboard Skateboard Truck', 31, 'https://www.muirskate.com/photos/products/7607/hd_product_Gullwing-Sidewinder-II-Black-%28Pair-HD%29.png', 'If you are looking for exaggerated easy turning and a smooth flow, the Gullwing Sidewinders are definitely the trucks for you. Designed to surf the street, the Gullwing Sidewinders simulate the movements that are common to surfing on an actually wave in the ocean! Surfing the desert is now possible!'),
('truck', '165mm Arsenal Raw Cast Longboard Skateboard Truck', 28, 'https://www.muirskate.com/photos/products/7538/hd_product_Arsenal-180mm-50deg-Raw-Truck-%28Set-HD%29.png', 'Arsenal has designed a new high performance cast trucks with freeriding and downhill in mind. These trucks come in two different baseplate angles 44° and 50° so you can mix and match to dial in your ride. The hanger is Flipable with Custom Kingpin Hole Geometry to Maximize Bushing Contact. Arsenals cast trucks are constructed out of Heat Treated to a T6 Temper and the axles are hardened steel, making these trucks unbelievably strong'),
